            "title": "A window to the world of global insect declines: Moth biodiversity trends are complex and heterogeneous",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "David L.",
                    "lastName": "Wagner"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
