            "itemType": "preprint",
            "title": "Effect of landscape tree cover, sex and season on the bioaccumulation of persistent organochlorine pesticides in fruit bats of riparian corridors in eastern Mexico",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
