            "title": "Direct PCR-DGGE Technique Reveals Wrinkle-Lipped Free-Tailed Bat (Chaerephon plicatus Buchanan, 1800) Predominantly Consume Planthoppers and Mosquitoes in Central Thailand",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Kantima",
                    "lastName": "Thongjued"
                },
